<div class="highlight">
	<div class="smaller-container">
		<h6 class="case-study__title">THE WORK</h6>
		<h2 class="case-study__question">A tailored discovery path</h2>
		<p class="case-study__content">
			With more than 100 video classes to chose from, Yoga para Mi’s new customers might have a hard time picking a first class. Also, different subscribers might be looking for more or less advanced clases, as well as different Yoga styles. To address that, we created a super-simple onboarding survey, that gets the visitor’s personal preferences and recommends a perfect match for their free class.
		</p>
